{
  "stem": "3952.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I-- I took the best pair of shoes when we go away from home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And somebody offered me a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I could have had a bite of bread then and there, but I said, I'm not going to give away. 10 minutes later, I left them there with the shoes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You had to pile everything separately, the shoes separately, your valises separately, your glasses separately, everything separate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you undressed completely, and they checked you out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they took you to a bath where they disinfected you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then you had to emerge yourself underneath.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You couldn't walk out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A kind of a mikvah, like a little pool, the size of a mikvah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And everyone in the line, you went in from this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You had to immerse yourself, and then you would go out the other-- the other side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then they gave you a pajama, which was [INAUDIBLE], which was a kind of a cap.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the stripes, a shirt and a pair of pants, and a pair of Holland sandals, wooden sandals this go click, click, click.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Those kind of sandals they gave us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when we all-- we were all dressed, so-called dressed, and we were hoping that now they will put us somewhere to rest.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They took us into a barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then you heard the blockalteste, which was a huge guy, looking like some prize fighter, which he probably was, because they took the strongest ones and the ugliest ones and the frightening ones.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he kept his short speech.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he said, if one of you asks me for toilet paper, I kill him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
